  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Pest Control Technician",
  "description": "<p> Join Our Team as a Pest Control Technician! </p><p>Are you hands-on, proactive, and love solving problems onthe spot? Do you enjoy keeping homes and businesses safe and pest-free? We are on the lookout for a reliable and enthusiastic Pest Control Technician to join our fast-growing team!</p><p><strong>What You will Do:</strong></p><ul><li>Inspect residential and commercial properties to identify pest issues and provide effective solutions.</li><li>Safely and efficiently apply pesticides, baits, and other control measures.</li><li>Keep accurate records of all treatments and activities.</li><li>Share friendly advice with clients on pest prevention and best practices.</li><li>Follow safety and environmental regulations to the letter.</li></ul><p><strong>What We are Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 1 year of experience as a pest control technician or worker.</li><li>Physically fit and comfortable working indoors and outdoors.</li><li>Basic English communication skills (spoken and written).</li><li>Valid Class 3 driving license.</li></ul><p><strong>Why You will Love Working With Us:</strong></p><ul><li>NEA courses & training fully sponsored by the company</li><li>Company vehicle + petrol card provided</li><li>Welcome Bonus $600 <em>(Terms & conditions apply)</em></li><li>Sundays Off – Work-Life Balance guaranteed!</li></ul><p>Call us NOW at <strong>+65 8975 6509 / +65 8807 4394</strong> to apply.</p>",
