    "description": "<p>Since 1985, <strong>GreenGarden Integrated Services Pte. Ltd.</strong> has been providing exceptional cleaning and landscaping services across Singapore. From commercial cleaning to landscaping maintenance and building upkeep, we take pride in delivering <strong>quality, reliability, and outstanding customer service</strong>.</p><p>At GreenGarden, we believe in <strong>investing in our people</strong>—equipping our staff with the skills, knowledge, and mindset to grow and succeed. Join us and be part of a team that values <strong>professionalism, teamwork, and continuous learning</strong>.</p><p>We are proud to be recognized as a <strong>BizSAFE Enterprise Level STAR</strong>, holders of the <strong>Clean Mark Silver Logo</strong>, and <strong>ISO certified</strong>, reflecting our strong commitment to <strong>safety, quality, and operational excellence</strong>.</p><p><strong>Take the next step in your career with a company that truly cares—join GreenGarden Integrated Services today!</strong></p>",
